reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Holy cow this comes with so much stuff! This little stationary set is so fun and if you are a fan of Sanrio at all, then this kit is for you. It comes with four different sets of sticky notes and you get a good amount of sticky notes with them. The pencil holder is super cute and well-made. The fabric is nice and thick. It doesn’t seem like it will rip at all. The little notebook is so adorable. I love all the different pictures of cinnamaroll. he is absolutely adorable. Pens work well. Not my favorite, but the design makes up for any lack of ink.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute, but not impressed with pencil case holding capabilities
reviews.reviewText: This set is basically a stationery bundle of Sanrio characters.For those who are not familiar with Sanrio, it mostly focuses on Hello Kitty's friends.Cinamoroll, Kuromi, My Melody. The set is really of a decent value.You get one notebook which is imho between an A6/A5 size notebook, a pack of pens that write closer to a medium point and thankfully they didn't get damaged in the transit. You get 4 little notepads of different characters that are by Sanrio.The claim that the pen case holds a large capacity is not true. it's more closer to a medium amount.It is perfect for those kids/adults who like Sanrio characters and for those who are into the "Kawaii" Journalism trend that is gaining popularity in the journalism and writing communities.Anyway, for the value these are a good mix together, but I just wasn't too impressed with the pen case holding capabilities are not a large amount of pens/pencils as one would think. So, that's why I took off a star over.
